notesStmt.note: This conversation occurs between two people, a couple, while they are preparing dinner at their home. They speak about the TV that was not delivered, about S2's sister and about a common friend. They start a discussion about a TV company and S2 decides to try a new TV company, which S1 does not seem to agree with. The atmosphere is casual and intimate.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
